item.title: Adding Custom Items
item.dc:creator: @jake_93 jake_93
item.description:
@jake_93 wrote:

You need to add the model of the item that you want to add into your models folder.
Then you want to add the int witht all the other item ints in your class8.java file.
Compile your server.

Also at some point through doing all that u need to log on and type a code, i think its add models but not sure exactly when u do tht. I think you do it after you add the models into the models folder.

Hope i could help,
Jake
